		<title>MURIEL speaks with Dr David Burleson, formerly of UNESCO-UNICEF, now UN Poet – Part 2</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UnitedNationsYak/~3/8rXPVVUIDoI/</link>
