<p align="left">  <strong>A Special 2012 New Year Message message in English and in French. </strong></td>
<td>
<img class="alignleft" style="margin-left: 4px; margin-right: 4px;" title="Cheick Sidi Diarra" src="http://yaktivate.s3.amazonaws.com/unitednationsyak/images/CheickSidiDiarra.jpg" alt="" width="140" height="163" /> </td>
