			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Muriel is rebroadcasting Dr Swaminathan&#8217;s New Year&#8217;s message to farmers of the world and his best wishes to farmers still suffering the consequences of the earthquake 2years after.</p>
<table border="0" align="center">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><a href="http://yaktivate.s3.amazonaws.com/unitednationsyak/audio/Dr.swaminathan100112F.mp3" target="_blank"><img style="width: 102px; height: 32px;" title="Listen Now" src="http://yaktivate.s3.amazonaws.com/images/button-listennow.gif" alt="Listen Now" hspace="10" width="102" height="32" align="left" /></a></td>
<td><a title="Subscribe to United Nations Yak" href="http://feeds2.feedburner.com/UnitedNationsYak" target="_blank"><img style="width: 112px; height: 32px;" src="http://yaktivate.s3.amazonaws.com/images/button-subscribe.gif" alt="" hspace="10" width="112" height="32" align="middle" /></a></td>
<td><a title="YAK" href="http://unitednationsyak.groupsite.com/discussion/forums" target="_blank"><img style="margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px;" src="http://yaktivate.s3.amazonaws.com/generalimages/discussionbutton.jpg" alt="" width="152" height="32" /></a></td>
</tr>
